44:  * A {@code ResolvedFxVanillaOption} is bound to data that changes over time, such as holiday calendars.
45:  * If the data changes, such as the addition of a new holiday, the resolved form will not be updated.
46:  * Care must be taken when placing the resolved form in a cache or persistence layer.
