117:    * This is the put/call for the base currency.
118:    * If the amount for the base currency is positive, the option is a call on the base currency (put on counter currency). 
119:    * If the amount for the base currency is negative, the option is a put on the base currency (call on counter currency).
120:    * 
121:    * @return the put or call
122:    */
123:   public PutCall getPutCall() {
124:     return underlying.getCounterCurrencyPayment().getAmount() > 0d ? PutCall.PUT : PutCall.CALL;
125:   }
