  "text": "## FxVanillaOption Type Family Trace\n\n### 1. Core Joda-Beans Domain Classes (modules/product/)\n\nThe four core domain classes form the primary type hierarchy for FX vanilla options:\n\n- **FxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java): The core vanilla FX option product class annotated with @BeanDefinition. It implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxVanillaOption>. Contains properties for longShort, expiryDate, expiryTime, expiryZone, and underlying FxSingle.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java): A trade wrapper around FxVanillaOption that implements FxOptionTrade and ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade>. Contains TradeInfo, product, and premium (AdjustablePayment).\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java): The resolved form of FxVanillaOption for pricing. Implements ResolvedProduct. Contains longShort, expiry (ZonedDateTime), and underlying (ResolvedFxSingle).\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java): The resolved form of FxVanillaOptionTrade. Implements ResolvedTrade. Contains TradeInfo, product (ResolvedFxVanillaOption), and premium (Payment).\n\n### 2. Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\n\nThe OpenGamma Strata codebase implements two main pricing models for FxVanillaOption, with separate product and trade pricers:\n\n**Black Model Pricers:**\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using the Black (lognormal) model.\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Black volatilities.\n\n**Vanna-Volga Model Pricers:**\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using the Vanna-Volga model.\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Vanna-Volga volatilities with smile.\n\n### 3. Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\n\nThe calculation layer wires pricers to the multi-scenario calculation engine:\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java): Multi-scenario calculation class holding references to BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer. Implements methods for presentValue, pv01, currencyExposure, delta, and vegaMarketQuoteBucketed.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java): High-level calculations API that wraps FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations and provides convenience methods for pricing and risk measures.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java): Implements CalculationFunction<FxVanillaOptionTrade> for integration with the Strata calculation engine. Maps measures (PresentValue, PV01, CurrencyExposure, etc.) to calculation methods.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMethod** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java): Enum (BLACK, VANNA_VOLGA) implementing CalculationParameter that allows users to specify which pricing method to use.\n\n### 4. Loader CSV Plugin (modules/loader/)\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin** (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java): Implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade>. Handles reading and writing FX vanilla option trades in CSV format with fields for long/short, put/call, strike, expiry, currency pair, notional, and premium.\n\n### 5. Related Type: FxSingleBarrierOption (modules/product/)\n\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java): A related product that embeds FxVanillaOption as a dependency (underlyingOption property). Implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxSingleBarrierOption>. The barrier option wraps a vanilla option with barrier and rebate specifications.\n\n### Type Resolution Chain\n\nThe flow follows this pattern:\n1. **Trade Creation**: User creates FxVanillaOptionTrade with FxVanillaOption and premium\n2. **Resolution**: FxVanillaOptionTrade#resolve() converts to ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade with ResolvedFxVanillaOption\n3. **Pricing**: BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer or VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer#presentValue() prices the resolved trade\n4. **Calculations**: FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations orchestrates pricers for multiple measures\n5. **Engine Integration**: FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction integrates with Strata's multi-scenario calculation engine\n\n### Key Design Patterns\n\n- **Product vs Trade**: Clear separation between the financial product (option terms) and the trade (position and premium)\n- **Unresolved vs Resolved**: Unresolved types (FxVanillaOption, FxVanillaOptionTrade) are used by business logic, while resolved types are bound to market data (calendars, rates) for pricing\n- **Pricer Variants**: Multiple pricing models (Black, Vanna-Volga) available through same interface\n- **Dual Abstraction Levels**: Product pricers handle pure valuation, trade pricers handle premium adjustments\n- **CSV Loading**: Standardized CSV format for importing trades via TradeCsvLoaderTest integration"
